### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Content-Type: application/json

### 默认插值 (三次样条)
POST http://localhost:8080/interpolate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {"x": 0, "y": 0},
    {"x": 1, "y": 1},
    {"x": 2, "y": 4},
    {"x": 3, "y": 9}
  ],
  "target_x_list": [0.5, 1.5, 2.5]
}

### 显式指定三次样条插值 (自然边界)
POST http://localhost:8080/interpolate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {"x": 0, "y": 1},
    {"x": 1, "y": 2},
    {"x": 2, "y": 1},
    {"x": 3, "y": 0},
    {"x": 4, "y": 1},
    {"x": 5, "y": 2}
  ],
  "target_x_list": [0.5, 1.5, 2.5, 3.5, 4.5],
  "method": "spline"
}

### 拉格朗日插值 (分段，避免Runge现象)
POST http://localhost:8080/interpolate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {"x": 0, "y": 0},
    {"x": 1, "y": 1},
    {"x": 2, "y": 4},
    {"x": 3, "y": 9},
    {"x": 4, "y": 16},
    {"x": 5, "y": 25},
    {"x": 6, "y": 36},
    {"x": 7, "y": 49},
    {"x": 8, "y": 64},
    {"x": 9, "y": 81}
  ],
  "target_x_list": [2.5, 4.5, 6.5],
  "method": "lagrange"
}

### 两种插值方法对比 - Runge现象测试
POST http://localhost:8080/interpolate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {"x": -5, "y": 0.0385},
    {"x": -4, "y": 0.0588},
    {"x": -3, "y": 0.1},
    {"x": -2, "y": 0.2},
    {"x": -1, "y": 0.5},
    {"x": 0, "y": 1},
    {"x": 1, "y": 0.5},
    {"x": 2, "y": 0.2},
    {"x": 3, "y": 0.1},
    {"x": 4, "y": 0.0588},
    {"x": 5, "y": 0.0385}
  ],
  "target_x_list": [-4.5, -2.5, -0.5, 0.5, 2.5, 4.5],
  "method": "spline"
}

### 自动去重 + 样条插值
POST http://localhost:8080/interpolate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {"x": 0, "y": 0},
    {"x": 0, "y": 0.5},
    {"x": 1, "y": 1},
    {"x": 1.000000001, "y": 1.1},
    {"x": 2, "y": 4},
    {"x": 3, "y": 9},
    {"x": 3, "y": 10}
  ],
  "target_x_list": [0.5, 1.5, 2.5],
  "method": "spline"
}

### 正弦函数 - 样条插值
POST http://localhost:8080/interpolate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {"x": 0, "y": 0},
    {"x": 0.7854, "y": 0.7071},
    {"x": 1.5708, "y": 1},
    {"x": 2.3562, "y": 0.7071},
    {"x": 3.1416, "y": 0},
    {"x": 4.7124, "y": -1},
    {"x": 6.2832, "y": 0}
  ],
  "target_x_list": [0.3927, 1.1781, 1.9635, 3.927, 5.4978],
  "method": "spline"
}

### 两点样条插值 (退化为线性)
POST http://localhost:8080/interpolate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {"x": 0, "y": 0},
    {"x": 10, "y": 100}
  ],
  "target_x_list": [2, 5, 8],
  "method": "spline"
}

### 不支持的插值方法 (错误测试)
POST http://localhost:8080/interpolate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": [
    {"x": 0, "y": 0},
    {"x": 1, "y": 1},
    {"x": 2, "y": 4}
  ],
  "target_x_list": [1.5],
  "method": "polynomial"
}
